== 袭击 ==
[[法新社|法新社]]称，三名全副武装的袭击者所袭击的旅馆为法国侨民所有。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/13/gunmen-open-fire-in-ivory-coast-tourist-resort|title=Gunmen open fire in Ivory Coast tourist resort|accessdate=13 March 2016|date=13 March 2016|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215095104/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/13/gunmen-open-fire-in-ivory-coast-tourist-resort}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-35798502|title=Ivory Coast: Shooting at Grand Bassam beach resort|accessdate=13 March 2016|date=13 March 2016|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122232556/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-35798502}}</ref><span class="mw-ref" id="cxcite_ref-7" rel="dc:references" contenteditable="false" data-sourceid="cite_ref-7"></span>官方称，共有15名游客和3名特种部队成员在袭击中遇难。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/14/africa/ivory-coast-attack/index.html|title=18 killed in attack on Ivory Coast hotels|website=CNN|access-date=2016-03-14|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414213344/https://www.cnn.com/2016/03/14/africa/ivory-coast-attack/index.html}}</ref>

根据目击者描述，袭击者身着便装，头戴[[巴拉克拉瓦头套|巴拉克拉瓦头套]]，装备了[[AK-47突击步枪|AK-47突击步枪]]和[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/cotedivoire/12192667/Ivory-Coast-hotel-shooting-Gunmen-open-fire-and-kill-11-in-beach-resort-Grand-Bassam-latest.html|title=Ivory Coast hotel shooting: Gunmen 'kill 15 including four Europeans' in Grand Bassam beach resort|website=Telegraph.co.uk|access-date=13 March 2016}}</ref> 袭击者在到达La Paillote旅馆后与警察交火。当地居民和游客被疏散至附近被临时关闭的旅馆。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://news.vice.com/article/gunmen-killed-12-people-at-a-resort-in-ivory-coast-officials-say|title=Gunmen Killed 14 People at a Beach Resort in Ivory Coast on Sunday|language=en-US|website=VICE News|access-date=13 March 2016|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314085354/https://news.vice.com/article/gunmen-killed-12-people-at-a-resort-in-ivory-coast-officials-say}}</ref>

[[美联社|美联社]]从科特迪瓦官员方面获悉，6名袭击者被击毙。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/latest-ivory-coast-beach-attackers-neutralized-37616977|title=The Latest: Ivory Coast Says 6 Beach Attackers 'Neutralized'|last=News|first=ABC|website=ABC News|access-date=13 March 2016|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314035058/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/latest-ivory-coast-beach-attackers-neutralized-37616977}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2016-03-13/the-latest-ivory-coast-says-6-beach-attackers-neutralized|title=Ivory Coast's government says that security forces have neutralized six armed men who staged attacks on three hotels in the historic town of Grand-Bassam|date=13 March 2016|website=US News & World Report|access-date=13 March 2016|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414213212/https://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2016-03-13/the-latest-ivory-coast-says-6-beach-attackers-neutralized}}</ref> 据传闻称，袭击者曾大喊“[[安拉胡阿克巴|安拉胡阿克巴]]”。<ref name="telegraph">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/cotedivoire/12192667/Ivory-Coast-hotel-shooting-Gunmen-open-fire-and-kill-11-in-beach-resort-Grand-Bassam-latest.html|title=Ivory Coast hotel shooting: Gunmen 'kill 12 including four Europeans' in Grand Bassam beach resort|accessdate=13 March 2016|website=Telegraph.co.uk|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514190106/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/cotedivoire/12192667/Ivory-Coast-hotel-shooting-Gunmen-open-fire-and-kill-11-in-beach-resort-Grand-Bassam-latest.html}}</ref> 袭击发生时，一个[[美国|美国]]大使代表团正在大巴萨姆逗留。但驻[[阿比让|阿比让]]的美国大使馆发布声明称，没有证据显示恐怖分子目标是美国公民，他们目前也没有接到美国公民伤亡的报告。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/ivory-coast-shooting-six-people-reportedly-dead-in-gun-attack-on-beach-resort-a6928756.html|title=12 people reportedly dead in gun attack on Ivory Coast beach resort popular with Western tourists|language=en-GB|website=The Independent|access-date=13 March 2016|archive-date=2020-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418175452/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/ivory-coast-shooting-six-people-reportedly-dead-in-gun-attack-on-beach-resort-a6928756.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/USEmbAbidjan/status/709047803054592000|title=U.S. Embassy Abidjan on Twitter|website=Twitter|access-date=13 March 2016|archive-date=2017-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170604174929/https://twitter.com/USEmbAbidjan/status/709047803054592000}}</ref>

[[伊斯兰马格里布基地组织|伊斯兰马格里布基地组织]](AQIM)和{{link-en|Al-Mourabitoun|Al-Mourabitoun (militant group)}}宣布对这起袭击负责。<ref name="Bloomberg">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-03-13/ivory-coast-beach-hotel-attack-said-to-leave-two-dead|title=Al-Qaeda Claims Ivory Coast Attack With At Least 16 Killed|date=13 March 2016|work=Bloomberg Business|accessdate=13 March 2016|last1=Mieu|first1=Baudelaire|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309152344/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-03-13/ivory-coast-beach-hotel-attack-said-to-leave-two-dead}}</ref> 3月17日，AQIM组织公布了袭击者名单：来自{{link-en|Al-Mourabitoun|Al-Mourabitoun (militant group)}}组织的 Hamza al-Fulani 和来自“沙漠之国”的 Abu Adam al-Ansari Abderrahmane al-Fulani 。<ref name="StarAfrica">{{Cite news|url=http://en.starafrica.com/news/aqim-releases-grand-bassam-attackers-photos.html|title=AQIM releases Grand-Bassam attackers’ photos|date=17 March 2016|work=StarAfrica|accessdate=17 March 2016|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322070059/http://en.starafrica.com/news/aqim-releases-grand-bassam-attackers-photos.html}}</ref>

